node.text: Alien Cookies f2 x Kush Mints 11

Thought I’d take it back to show you the Bubba Bx1 mother of Kush Mints. This was in my garage and the same run that made Wedding Cake, animal walker, animal face and many others. Now you see where kush mints gets her structure. Not the best pic, but this lady was pregnant with some legendary children and grandmother to strains like Georgia pie, Collins Ave, Ocean Beach, Grand Daddy Pluto, honey buns, pancakes, L.A kush Cake, and many more.
Let me know if you’re growing any of her progeny and what the cross is 🙏

Here we have Alien Cookies f2 selected by @capulator crossed with our Kush Mints 11 male. He shot me back half the beans, then we grew them out and selected this fine lady. Not many breeders can collaborate properly without screwing each other and I can say Cap is a stand up guy. Instead of renaming someone else’s cut we decided to breed something special that involves more work than usual to debut a proper collab. Good things take time🙏👊

Also, make sure to follow our only back up account @seedjunkygenetics_jbeezy

node.text:
This cross is epic! 🔥@powerzzzup @berner415 @theminntz 
Details are above

Just the tip of some Scotti’s Cake. 

Guys and gals, please don’t reply to fake Seed Junky accounts reaching out to you asking for money. We don’t work with them. They mimic my account with subtle changes that look real and some even have thousands of followers, but they aren’t to be trusted. Our only back up account is @seedjunkygenetics_jbeezy 

🙏👊

Here’s a new lady we have our eyes on…it’s EmergenC x Banana Cream Cake. It’s hard to capture how frosty she is but she definitely shines hard and is crazy loud. So far all Banana Cream Cake crosses have increased frost and yields. 🙏🔥

node.text: Here’s a few more in the testing room beginning from left to right-(Gelato 41 x Animal Mints) x Banana Cream Cake, Pineapple Fruz x Banana Cream Cake, and (Gelato 41 x Animal Mints) x (Biscotti x Sherb bx1 x Jealousy). In advance, this is just the lineage not the names. Pics were taken mid week 7.
From left to right Gelato 41 x Banana Cream Cake, EmergenC x Banana Cream Cake, and Pineapple Fruz x Banana Cream Cake.

node.text: TGIF! Here we have some new ladies in the pheno hunting room. 1st up is (Orange push pop x wedding cake f3) x (biscotti x Sherb bx x jealousy) and second is Scotti’s Cake which has a crazy gassy nose thus far. Enjoy your weekends dank lovers. For the grinders, I’m sure you’ll continue working throughout the weekend, big props to those that never stop ✋ 🙏👊

node.text:
Popping off a new mother room at our SoCal. Nursery, with @photobioled which really helps us keep our humidity optimal for our mommy’s. 
Our mission is to spread the 🔥as far as possible while we’re here. Grow with us 🙏👊
Cultivators all the info is in our Bio.
From the R&D room we have Scotti’s Cake, and two different Pineapple Fruz x Banana Cream Cake phenos. This Scotti’s Cake is so damn gassy and frosty. It’s hard to get a proper photo of her 🙏
